data.name: containerAListView.ToolTip
data.value: If you want you can select files and then copy them to the container on the right. If you do nothing and just click on "Copy" then the amount of files as shown in the "Max files box" will be copied.

data.name: saveButton.ToolTip
data.value:
Save all the files in the blue-box on your Tyros HD. The total number of files will be extracted from the first white list-box.
Keep in mind that a directory can contain max 500 files, otherwise you will get an error while reading that directory on your keyboard.

data.name: ExtensieComboBox.ToolTip
data.value: Some extensions are pre-defined. You can enter the extension your looking for: f.i. Style Files - sty, pst, pcs, sst, prs, bcs, fps Registration Files - rgt, reg Music Finder Files - mfd Voice Files - org, vce, liv, swv, clv, mgv, sar, ldr, drm
